nt/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">Element <strong><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></strong> SVG określa hiperłącze.</span></p>\n\n<p>Element<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"> &lt;a&gt; </a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\">HTML </a>jest interpretowany tak samo jak element &lt;a&gt; SVG. Z tego względu w przypadku użycia selektora &lt;a&gt; w CSS lub JavaScript może mieć zastosowanie do nieprawidłowego elementu. Wypróbuj regułę @namespace, aby rozróżnić między nimi.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"użycie","title":"Użycie","isH3":false,"content":"<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\">Categories</th><td>Container element</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Permitted content</th><td>Any number of the following elements, in any order:<br><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/SVG/Element#animation_elements\">Animation elements</a><br><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/SVG/Element#descriptive_elements\">Descriptive elements</a><br><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/SVG/Element#shape_elements\">Shape elements</a><br><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/SVG/Element#structural_elements\">Structural elements</a><br><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/SVG/Element#gradient_elements\">Gradient elements</a><br><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/SVG/Element/a\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code>